    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>烁光暗影</strong>是一款第一人称砍杀类动作肉鸽游戏，背景设定在一个黑暗奇幻世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时空穿越</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/dbe74f0fd9eddd9be0fcdb1bd27a6c07.poster.avif?t=1760098852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/dbe74f0fd9eddd9be0fcdb1bd27a6c07.webm?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/dbe74f0fd9eddd9be0fcdb1bd27a6c07.mp4?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于过去于现在之间，一路砍杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >凶残的砍杀战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/47e28f2fa48cd95f589ff3adc6dda091.poster.avif?t=1760098852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/47e28f2fa48cd95f589ff3adc6dda091.webm?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/47e28f2fa48cd95f589ff3adc6dda091.mp4?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起各种近战及远程武器，在一波波的敌人中间杀出一条血路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多样的升级与构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/d6120f42f74359a53dd62e41c55a5add.poster.avif?t=1760098852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/d6120f42f74359a53dd62e41c55a5add.webm?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/d6120f42f74359a53dd62e41c55a5add.mp4?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择各种不同的升级来完成你最为完美的升级路线，或是最为奇怪的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >紧张刺激的Boss战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/9ab5cdfe7d126c87fbdccad50d9d80f2.poster.avif?t=1760098852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/9ab5cdfe7d126c87fbdccad50d9d80f2.webm?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287090/extras/9ab5cdfe7d126c87fbdccad50d9d80f2.mp4?t=1760098852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过挑战各种Boss来掌握战斗的秘诀。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
